<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 20:09:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>死者家属会见以色列国防军指挥官，指挥官下令用坦克向贝埃里基布兹的家开火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</link><description>基布兹的一份声明称，大多数遇难者家属在结束对话时都感到和解，并对哈马斯袭击期间基布兹发生的复杂局势有了更好的了解</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 19:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/families-of-killed-hostages-meet-with-idf-officer-who-ordered-tank-fire-on-kibbutz-home/00000191-045b-d117-abd9-8d7f73700000</guid></item><item><title>“他们向我吐口水，称我为荡妇”：记者在以色列国防军基地遭到极右暴徒袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</link><description>周一，右翼抗议者对前来报道斯德泰曼拘留中心袭击事件的一些以色列记者进行辱骂、吐口水和人身攻击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:41:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/they-spit-on-me-called-me-a-slut-journalists-attacked-by-far-right-mob-at-idf-base/00000191-0461-dc27-abdb-f6714c350000</guid></item><item><title>要成为一个文明国家，以色列必须承认自己的野蛮行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡不能两全其美。他不能试图将以色列描绘成一个开明的民主国家，保卫自己（和西方世界）免受残酷怪物的侵害，同时也容忍那些不认为应该调查针对可能的恐怖分子的野蛮行为的部长</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 18:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/to-be-a-civilized-nation-israel-must-acknowledge-its-own-barbarism/00000191-04b6-df85-a399-edb6e2860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 298 天：以色列国防军称其目标是真主党二号人物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</link><description>以色列平民被黎巴嫩火箭弹弹片炸死 ■ 以色列国防军消息人士称，被扣押在加沙的一些人质尸体将永远找不到袭击以色列国防军基地的右翼暴徒 ■ 据报道，英国已决定推迟停止向以色列出口武器的决定 ■ 战争进入 298 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 17:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-298-idf-says-it-targeted-hezbollahs-second-in-command/00000191-04a7-dc27-abdb-f6f7ca3b0000</guid></item><item><title>看到受虐待的加沙被拘留者的斯德·泰曼医生：“我不敢相信以色列狱警能做出这样的事”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/doctor-who-saw-abused-gazan-detainee-i-couldnt-believe-an-israeli-jailer-could-do-this/00000191-0436-df85-a399-ed36f4800000</link><description>斯德泰曼医院的医生约尔·唐钦教授在这名加沙被拘留者据称遭到九名以色列预备役军人虐待后见过他，他对该男子的状况表示震惊。 “我确信这是努赫巴人对努赫巴人的报复，”他说，指的是哈马斯精英部队</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:42:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/doctor-who-saw-abused-gazan-detainee-i-couldnt-believe-an-israeli-jailer-could-do-this/00000191-0436-df85-a399-ed36f4800000</guid></item><item><title>高级警官对以色列国防军基地的骚乱表示：“明确的政策是视而不见”； “本-格维尔不必说一句话”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/senior-police-officers-on-riots-at-idf-bases-the-clear-policy-was-to-turn-a-blind-eye/00000191-03c8-d117-abd9-8fef5fea0000</link><description>高级警察批评以色列警察部队在应对周一斯德泰曼和拜特利德骚乱时的行为，允许抗议者闯入基地。一位高级官员表示，“警察已经破产，没有指挥”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 16:29:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/senior-police-officers-on-riots-at-idf-bases-the-clear-policy-was-to-turn-a-blind-eye/00000191-03c8-d117-abd9-8fef5fea0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日之后：以色列考古学家创造了在战区寻找人类遗骸的方法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/after-oct-7-israeli-archaeologists-create-methodology-to-find-human-remains-in-war-zones/00000191-03f7-d3e8-adbd-bbf71c5d0000</link><description>当以色列考古学家在哈马斯袭击后加入搜寻失踪人员的行列时，他们运用了独特的训练方法，在遭到破坏、烧毁的地区寻找失踪的尸体。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/after-oct-7-israeli-archaeologists-create-methodology-to-find-human-remains-in-war-zones/00000191-03f7-d3e8-adbd-bbf71c5d0000</guid></item><item><title>“战争从来没有拯救过儿童。大多数德鲁兹人表示，他们不希望自己的悲剧引发更多杀戮”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-30/ty-article-podcast/war-never-saved-children-most-druze-dont-want-their-tragedy-to-cause-more-killing/00000191-0322-da0d-afd1-8bae4b7c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-30/ty-article-podcast/war-never-saved-children-most-druze-dont-want-their-tragedy-to-cause-more-killing/00000191-0322-da0d-afd1-8bae4b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部真主党猛攻后，一名男子被火箭弹碎片炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-by-rocket-shrapnel-in-northern-israel-following-hezbollah-barrage/00000191-03e8-d117-abd9-8fef2bef0000</link><description>两天前，戈兰高地 Majdal Shams 镇发生火箭弹袭击，导致 12 名儿童和青少年丧生，以色列称该镇是真主党所为，28 岁的尼尔·普普科 (Nir Pupko) 被杀。以色列尚未对周六的袭击做出回应</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 15:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/man-killed-by-rocket-shrapnel-in-northern-israel-following-hezbollah-barrage/00000191-03e8-d117-abd9-8fef2bef0000</guid></item><item><title>格兰特呼吁内塔尼亚胡调查本格维尔在警方对以色列国防军基地骚乱反应迟缓中所扮演的角色</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-netanyahu-probe-ben-gvirs-role-in-delayed-response-to-riots-at-idf-bases/00000191-0386-df85-a399-eb96270e0000</link><description>加兰特在一封信中告诉总理，“支持以色列国防军基地骚乱并积极参与骚乱的民选官员构成了损害国家安全的非常严重的危险”，敦促他“果断地解决这个问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-netanyahu-probe-ben-gvirs-role-in-delayed-response-to-riots-at-idf-bases/00000191-0386-df85-a399-eb96270e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对 Majdal Shams 有宏伟的计划。然后与真主党的战争开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-had-big-plans-for-majdal-shams-then-the-war-with-hezbollah-started/00000191-0388-d76c-abf3-d3eb8f550000</link><description>自叙利亚内战以来，戈兰高地德鲁兹派与以色列当局之间的关系有所升温，但加沙战争冻结了迈季代勒​​沙姆斯的计划，该镇周一遭到火箭袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-had-big-plans-for-majdal-shams-then-the-war-with-hezbollah-started/00000191-0388-d76c-abf3-d3eb8f550000</guid></item><item><title>如果真主党摧毁以色列的天然气钻井平台会发生什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-would-happen-if-hezbollah-destroys-israels-natural-gas-rigs/00000191-0352-d76c-abf3-d37bda330000</link><description>如果北部局势升级，真主党可能会瞄准以色列的天然气钻井平台。三个钻机全部关闭的情况是极端的，但也是有可能的。煤炭可以弥补部分缺口，但还不够</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-would-happen-if-hezbollah-destroys-israels-natural-gas-rigs/00000191-0352-d76c-abf3-d37bda330000</guid></item><item><title>我们警告过斯德·泰曼。那里的酷刑有高层支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-warned-about-harsh-treatment-at-sde-teiman-the-torture-there-has-backing-from-high-up/00000191-030c-dfce-a991-bf7d5cfa0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 12:13:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/we-warned-about-harsh-treatment-at-sde-teiman-the-torture-there-has-backing-from-high-up/00000191-030c-dfce-a991-bf7d5cfa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列要求北约国家反对埃尔多安威胁入侵该国边境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-nato-countries-to-object-erdogans-threat-to-invade-its-borders/00000191-02e8-d0f6-adf9-deec9d380000</link><description>没有北约成员国发表声明谴责埃尔多安的威胁；以色列-土耳其问题高级专家表示，言辞冲突和外交部长以色列·卡茨的推文正在“加剧危机”，而且土耳其没有任何克制的迹象</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-urges-nato-countries-to-object-erdogans-threat-to-invade-its-borders/00000191-02e8-d0f6-adf9-deec9d380000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队结束东汗尤尼斯攻势，巴勒斯坦人找到了数十具加沙人的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/israeli-forces-end-east-khan-yunis-offensive-as-palestinians-recover-dozens-of-bodies/00000191-0353-d76c-abf3-d37ba7c80000</link><description>加沙民事紧急服务部门表示，更多搜寻工作正在进行中，据报仍有 200 人失踪；以色列军队表示，其部队在大约一周的行动中击毙了 150 多名恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:23:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/israeli-forces-end-east-khan-yunis-offensive-as-palestinians-recover-dozens-of-bodies/00000191-0353-d76c-abf3-d37ba7c80000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的新以色列警察局长人选：阿拉伯谋杀率飙升和镇压抗议活动记录</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-record-of-cracking-down-on-protests-soaring-murder-rates/00000191-02d8-d0f6-adf9-dedc20e10000</link><description>在新任警察局长候选人丹尼·利维 (Danny Levy) 的领导下，沿海地区的谋杀率飙升，其中阿拉伯受害者人数增加，但侦破的案件却很少。利维还因严厉镇压反政府抗议者以及与极右翼部长本-格维尔的密切关系而闻名</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 11:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-record-of-cracking-down-on-protests-soaring-murder-rates/00000191-02d8-d0f6-adf9-dedc20e10000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔部官员因涉嫌发放枪支许可证以换取贿赂而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/official-in-ben-gvirs-ministry-arrested-on-suspicion-of-issuing-gun-permits-for-bribes/00000191-027f-dfce-a991-bf7fe0170000</link><description>警方怀疑伊塔马尔-本·格维尔部委的一名官员向数百名不符合持有枪支门槛标准的申请人发放了许可证。另外三名被捕人士涉嫌在双方之间进行调解</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/official-in-ben-gvirs-ministry-arrested-on-suspicion-of-issuing-gun-permits-for-bribes/00000191-027f-dfce-a991-bf7fe0170000</guid></item><item><title>慕尼黑之影：巴黎奥运会以色列代表团面临自1972年奥运会以来最高级别的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-to-paris-olympics-faces-highest-threat-level-since-1972-games/00000190-fed3-d88d-adb8-ffff92f90000</link><description>以色列辛贝特安全部门在加沙战争和50多年来最高威胁级别的背景下为奥运会做好了准备</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 09:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-to-paris-olympics-faces-highest-threat-level-since-1972-games/00000190-fed3-d88d-adb8-ffff92f90000</guid></item><item><title>英国新政府考虑对以色列实施武器禁运“违反国际法”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/new-british-govt-mulling-arms-embargo-against-israel-over-violations-of-international-law/00000191-01a1-d0f6-adf9-dfa5e48d0000</link><description>在国际法院裁定以色列西岸定居点非法后，新当选的工党政府可能会在几周内做出决定。唐宁街和耶路撒冷仍在就此事进行谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/new-british-govt-mulling-arms-embargo-against-israel-over-violations-of-international-law/00000191-01a1-d0f6-adf9-dfa5e48d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于野蛮的边缘：极右翼部长和联盟MK袭击军事基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/when-ministers-and-mks-storm-army-bases-israels-brutalization-is-nearly-complete/00000191-00ef-d76c-abf3-d2ef9e7e0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府的成员为极右翼暴徒提供了助力，他们袭击了斯德·泰曼并闯入营地。以色列国防军透明且依法运作的论点是针对认为以色列犯有战争罪的世界的最佳弹药</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/when-ministers-and-mks-storm-army-bases-israels-brutalization-is-nearly-complete/00000191-00ef-d76c-abf3-d2ef9e7e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>